 was mentioned in the spec, it is not yet present in the codebase (targeted for T-030), and the use of the `Event` model for these transformations is the correct adaptation for the current project state.\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+## Security\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+No security vulnerabilities or unsafe practices were introduced. The implementation consists of pure-function mathematical transformations on local data structures.\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+## Quality\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+The code quality is high, with clear documentation, clean dataclass abstractions, and robust role-parsing logic. The tests use Pearson correlation to verify complementarity, which is a rigorous approach for validating musical behavior.\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+## Issues Found\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+- None.\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+## Verdict: PASS\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+## Notes for Lead Agent\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+The implementation successfully realizes the call-response gating requirement. The adaptation to use the `Event` model in the absence of `PerformanceIntent` is appropriate. Recurring hardening checks for `bootstrap_identity` were also verified to be satisfied in the current daemon startup paths.\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"}\\\\\\\\n+{\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"type\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\":\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"message\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\",\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"timestamp\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\":\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"2026-04-17T04:06:12.389Z\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\",\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"role\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\":\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"assistant\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\",\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"content\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\":\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"I'll\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\",\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"delta\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\":true}\\\\\\\\n+{\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"type\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\":\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"message\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\",\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"timestamp\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\":\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"2026-04-17T04:06:12.406Z\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\",\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"role\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\":\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"assistant\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\",\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"content\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\":\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\" update `progress.md` to mark T-024 as complete and include the relevant logs, ensuring the SDP\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\",\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"delta\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\":true}\\\\\\\\n+\\\\\\\\n+codex\\\\\\\\n+The dirty state is entirely generated SDP tracking: progress, run logs, notifications, telemetry, and an untracked canonical T-024 verification report that complements an earlier misnamed report. I’m staging those artifacts now so the tree can be committed and left clean.\\\\\\\\n+exec\\\\\\\\n+/bin/zsh -lc 'git add -A' in /Users/anthony/Programming/PromptClaw\\\\\\\\n+ succeeded in 109ms:\\\\\\\\n+exec\\\\\\\\n+/bin/zsh -lc 'git status --short' in /Users/anthony/Programming/PromptClaw\\\\\\\\n+ succeeded in 0ms:\\\\\\\\n+M  progress.md\\\\\\\\n+M  sdp/logs/Lead_T-021_20260416T181925Zb_1776395654.log\\\\\\\\n+A  sdp/logs/Lead_T-021_20260416T181925Zc_1776395895.log\\\\\\\\n+A  sdp/logs/Lead_T-022_20260416T181925Z_1776396842.log\\\\\\\\n+A  sdp/logs/Lead_T-023_20260416T181925Z_1776397430.log\\\\\\\\n+A  sdp/logs/Lead_T-025_20260416T181925Z_1776398857.log\\\\\\\\n+A  sdp/logs/Lead_T-026_20260416T181925Z_1776399250.log\\\\\\\\n+A  sdp/logs/Lead_T-027_20260416T181925Z_1776399901.log\\\\\\\\n+A  sdp/logs/Lead_T-028_20260416T181925Z_1776400429.log\\\\\\\\n+A  sdp/logs/Lead_T-029_20260416T181925Z_1776400962.log\\\\\\\\n+A  sdp/logs/Lead_T-030_20260416T181925Z_1776401478.log\\\\\\\\n+A  sdp/logs/Lead_T-031_20260416T181925Z_1776401815.log\\\\\\\\n+A  sdp/logs/Lead_T-032_20260416T181925Z_1776402396.log\\\\\\\\n+A  sdp/logs/Lead_T-033_20260416T181925Z_1776402787.log\\\\\\\\n+A  sdp/logs/Lead_T-034_20260416T181925Z_1776403295.log\\\\\\\\n+A  sdp/logs/Lead_T-035_20260416T181925Z_1776403697.log\\\\\\\\n+A  sdp/logs/Lead_T-035_20260416T181925Z_1776404297.log\\\\\\\\n+A  sdp/logs/Lead_T-035_20260416T181925Z_1776404481.log\\\\\\\\n+M  sdp/logs/Verify_T-021_20260416T181925Zb_1776395753.log\\\\\\\\n+A  sdp/logs/Verify_T-021_20260416T181925Zc_1776396511.log\\\\\\\\n+A  sdp/logs/Verify_T-022_20260416T181925Z_1776397313.log\\\\\\\\n+A  sdp/logs